node_modules/vendors/readme

vendors

![Build][build-badge] ![Downloads][downloads-badge] ![Size][size-badge]

List of (real†) vendor prefixes known to the web platform. From Wikipedia and the CSS 2.1 spec.

† — real, as in, mso- and prince- are not included because they are not valid.

Installation

npm:

npm install vendors

Usage

var vendors = require('vendors')

console.log(vendors)

Yields:

[ 'ah',
  'apple',
  'atsc',
  'epub',
  'hp',
  'khtml',
  'moz',
  'ms',
  'o',
  'rim',
  'ro',
  'tc',
  'wap',
  'webkit',
  'xv' ]
